@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_qhxcin(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.sin(v2))
    tmp = wp.sin(0.65)
    tmp = 0.92
    v0 = ((wp.exp(v2 + 0.52) * wp.abs(tmp + 0.76)) - 0.95)
    v0 = (wp.cos(wp.abs(v1 + 0.54)) - ((v0 + 0.04 + tmp + 0.05) - wp.cos(v1 + 0.77)))
    data[tid] = v0
